name: Attack
note:
<Weapon Range>

<Setup Action>
display action
immortal: targets, true
</Setup Action>

<Whole Action>
if user.attackMotion() === "missile"
  move user: forward, 20
  wait for movement
end
</Whole Action>

<Target Action>
if user.attackMotion() !== "missile"
  move user: target, front base, 24
  wait for movement
end
motion attack: user
motion wait: user
if user.attackMotion() === "missile"
  se: CrossBow
  projectile user: target, icon 416; angle -45; arc 30; speed 50; end anim 11; wait
  wait for projectiles
else
  attack animation: target
  wait for animation
end
action effect: target
</Target Action>
